import React from 'react'; import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'; import formatToCurrency from '../../../utils/formatToCurrency'; import generateBankImageUrl from './generateBankImageUrl'; import styles from './FundsTransferCompleted.module.scss'; var Barcode = require('react-barcode'); export const FundsTransferCompleted = (props) => { const { successData, setComponentToRender, FundsTransferFormState } = props; const { beneficiaryBankName, amount, accountNumber, accountName, total, beneficiaryBankCode, } = FundsTransferFormState; const { date, transactionCost, status, reference, agentCode } = successData; const bankImageUrl = generateBankImageUrl(beneficiaryBankCode); return (
Payment Reference: {reference}
Beneficiary Bank: {beneficiaryBankName}
Beneficiary Name: {accountName}
Beneficiary Account: {accountNumber}
Status: {status}
Agent Code: {agentCode}
Date: {date}
Amount: ₦{formatToCurrency(amount)}
Convenience Fee: ₦{formatToCurrency(transactionCost)}
Total: ₦{formatToCurrency(total)}
window.print()} > Print
); }; export default FundsTransferCompleted;
